<refentry id="bif.SetStrategyProb" xreflabel="SetStrategyProb">

<refmeta>
<indexterm>
<primary>SetStrategyProb</primary>
</indexterm>

<refentrytitle>SetStrategyProb</refentrytitle>
<refmiscinfo>Built-in function</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
<refname>SetStrategyProb</refname>
<refpurpose>
Sets the probability a strategy is played in a profile
</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
SetStrategyProb[profile<->MIXED, strategy->STRATEGY, 
                value->NUMBER] =: MIXED 
</synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1><title>Description</title>
<para>
<function>SetStrategyProb</function>
sets the component of <parameter>profile</parameter> for 
<parameter>strategy</parameter> to be equal
to <parameter>value</parameter>.  It is an error if <parameter>profile</parameter> and <parameter>strategy</parameter>
are not from the same normal form game.  Returns <parameter>profile</parameter>.
</para>
</refsect1>

